{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<label>","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"\n  <ol>\n   \n            <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a></li>\n  \n            <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/datalist\"><code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code></a></li>\n  \n            <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></a></li>\n  \n            <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code></a></li>\n  \n            <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/legend\"><code>&lt;legend&gt;</code></a></li>\n  \n            <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a></li>\n  \n            <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code></a></li>\n  \n            <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code></a></li>\n  \n            <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></a></li>\n  \n            <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  \n    \n   <li><details><summary>HTML Elements</summary><ol>\n   <li>A\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/acronym\"><code>&lt;acronym&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/applet\"><code>&lt;applet&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/area\"><code>&lt;area&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;arti